文の宿題、", "ちゃんとやって", "きたかな"]}, {"box": [81, 670, 98, 714], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23, "lines_coords": [[[81.0, 670.0], [98.0, 670.0], [98.0, 714.0], [81.0, 714.0]]], "lines": ["ー？"]}, {"box": [892, 1103, 1029, 1284], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[1004.0, 1106.0], [1026.0, 1106.0], [1026.0, 1260.0], [1004.0, 1260.0]], [[964.0, 1104.0], [992.0, 1104.0], [993.0, 1243.0], [965.0, 1243.0]], [[926.0, 1103.0], [954.0, 1103.0], [956.0, 1284.0], [928.0, 1284.0]], [[892.0, 1104.0], [918.0, 1104.0], [918.0, 1273.0], [892.0, 1273.0]]], "lines": ["きのう午前中", "全部使って、", "みんな一人ずつ", "発表しました。"]}, {"box": [534, 809, 674, 995], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30, "lines_coords": [[[643.0, 809.0], [671.0, 809.0], [673.0, 995.0], [645.0, 995.0]], [[609.0, 809.0], [640.0, 809.0], [637.0, 995.0], [606.0, 995.0]], [[573.0, 812.0], [600.0, 812.0], [600.0, 993.0], [573.0, 993.0]], [[534.0, 809.0], [567.0, 809.0], [567.0, 901.0], [534.0, 901.0]]], "lines": ["突然だったので", "プンプンは少し", "動揺してしまい", "ました。"]}, {"box": [390, 776, 417, 961], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27, "lines_coords": [[[390.0, 776.0], [417.0, 776.0], [417.0, 887.0], [390.0, 887.0]]], "lines": ["どしたー"]}, {"box": [687, 1334, 788, 1543], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[760.0, 1334.0], [787.0, 1334.0], [787.0, 1467.0], [760.0, 1467.0]], [[725.0, 1335.0], [751.0, 1335.0], [751.0, 1493.0], [725.0, 1493.0]], [[687.0, 1334.0], [714.0, 1334.0], [715.0, 1542.0], [689.0, 1542.0]]], "lines": ["プンプンも", "みんなの前で", "発表しましょう！！"]}, {"box": [112, 1346, 214, 1529], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[185.0, 1346.0], [214.0, 1346.0], [214.0, 1481.0], [185.0, 1481.0]], [[148.0, 1350.0], [175.0, 1350.0], [175.0, 1529.0], [148.0, 1529.0]], [[112.0, 1348.0], [139.0, 1348.0], [139.0, 1443.0], [112.0, 1443.0]]], "lines": ["もしかして", "やってきてない", "のかなー"]}, {"box": [115, 1457, 137, 1504], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[115.0, 1457.0], [137.0, 1457.0], [137.0, 1504.0], [115.0, 1504.0]]], "lines": ["．．．"]}], "img_path": "036.png"}, {"version": "0.2.0-beta.6", "img_width": 1100, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [893, 31, 1126, 633], "vertical": true, "font_size": 183, "lines_coords": [[[943.0, 31.0], [1126.0, 37.0], [1107.0, 626.0], [925.0, 620.0]]], "lines": ["フゥオアアァァァ"]}, {"box": [20, 41, 212, 531], "vertical": true, "font_size": 192, "lines_coords": [[[20.0, 41.0], [212.0, 41.0], [212.0, 531.0], [20.0, 531.0]]], "lines": ["アァアアァァォ！！！"]}, {"box": [885, 915, 1031, 1229], "vertical": true, "font_size": 38, "lines_coords": [[[982.0, 915.0], [1026.0, 915.0], [1031.0, 1162.0], [987.0, 1162.0]], [[932.0, 917.0], [976.0, 917.0], [976.0, 1229.0], [932.0, 1229.0]], [[885.0, 920.0], [918.0, 920.0], [918.0, 1179.0], [885.0, 1179.0]]], "lines": ["んっ、駄目じゃ", "ないか、宿題やって", "こなきゃああ！！"]}, {"box": [918, 1251, 1003, 1367], "vertical": true, "font_size": 38, "lines_coords": [[[918.0, 1251.0], [953.0, 1251.0], [953.0, 1367.0], [918.0, 1367.0]], [[968.0, 1264.0], [1003.0, 1264.0], [1003.0, 1365.0], [968.0, 1365.0]]], "lines": ["だっ！！", "んっ！！"]}, {"box": [868, 1370, 910, 1540], "vertical": true, "font_size": 38, "lines_coords": [[[871.0, 1370.0], [910.0, 1370.0], [907.0, 1540.0], [868.0, 1540.0]]], "lines": ["フゥオオ"]}, {"box": [812, 1371, 906, 1581], "vertical": true, "font_size": 38, "lines_coords": [[[812.0, 1371.0], [850.0, 1371.0], [853.0, 1581.0], [815.0, 1581.0]]], "lines": ["オオオッ！！"]}, {"box": [382, 1215, 550, 1570], "vertical": true, "font_size": 37, "lines_coords": [[[514.0, 1215.0], [548.0, 1215.0], [545.0, 1439.0], [510.0, 1439.0]], [[467.0, 1215.0], [504.0, 1215.0], [506.0, 1570.0], [468.0, 1570.0]], [[417.0, 1217.0], [460.0, 1217.0], [465.0, 1515.0], [421.0, 1515.0]], [[382.0, 1218.0], [414.0, 1218.0], [414.0, 1440.0], [382.0, 1440.0]]], "lines": ["どんな事情が", "あっても、やらなきゃ", "いけないんだよォ", "オオオォッ！！"]}], "img_path": "037.png"}, {"version": "0.2.0-beta.6", "img_width": 1100, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [900, 120, 1000, 329], "vertical": true,